{"tid":1228034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢刻就好似有個親人離開左咁","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:20:31.000Z","uid":84396,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef22683f0b86ba96b06b0dcee73e1fec03acc567","tid":1228034,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"諗返果日發夢 我地一齊搬野 一齊擔遮 一齊捉住前面背囊<br />\n一齊衝 一齊退 中左招扶住大家走<br />\n<br />\n估唔到過左兩日 係現實中你竟然咁就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你比親人更親 因為我既親人呢一世都唔可能同我有過咁既經歷 一齊同生共死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔應該離開我地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬥長命我地贏硬架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講好左要一齊睇住班仆街不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已經講到1999 Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唯有夢中再相聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足們 我地黎緊兩日一齊發個好夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實現呢位親如親人戰友既遺願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761f9e1144e9e0096ceb3df9f147264c452f2b36","tid":1228034,"uid":84396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:12:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />討回公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f1aade3ee09c77a987a89ecb604de03c94b042","tid":1228034,"uid":84396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />討回公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5d55013d8d34310eaac1287e588ed36e39d220","